Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.58,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,握ったメッセージ　That's Rising Hope
Comment: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:05.20,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,(Welcome to message crazy)
Comment: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.08,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,(Can you distance stand by)
Comment: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:07.86,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,(Here we go)
Comment: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.26,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,揺るがない世界　異常な幻聴
Comment: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.56,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,綴った手は　Rising soul
Comment: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.98,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,イメージ通りなんかじゃない
Comment: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.32,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,静かに騒ぎだした本能
Comment: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.44,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,迷路みたい　行き止まりなんて
Comment: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.70,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,でも思考は　Distortion
Comment: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:30.10,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,容赦ないね　いつの間に
Comment: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.64,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,見失ってると暴れだす
Comment: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:35.28,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,Hey one two three
Comment: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:38.40,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,常識なんていらない
Comment: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.08,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,no no no Don't worry
Comment: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:40.88,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,one two three
Comment: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.94,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,動き出す心臓のリズム
Comment: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:45.38,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,視界まだ眩んでる
Comment: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:48.32,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,それでも　行かなくちゃ
Comment: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:53.54,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,君が信じてる僕を　裏切る
Comment: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:57.50,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,わけにいかない　強くクラクションが鳴る
Comment: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:01.24,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,孤独なまま時が経ったって
Comment: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:03.62,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,逃げる事覚えたって
Comment: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:06.88,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,新しい今日が来ちゃうけど
Comment: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:11.32,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,この願い　例え魔法がなくたって
Comment: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:13.50,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,叶えなきゃ誓った
Comment: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:16.74,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,僕は君と　まだ見たい未来あるんだよ
Comment: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.34,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,泣きそうでも
Comment: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:23.38,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,悔しくても　止まっていられない
Comment: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:26.86,SAO3-OP2-yk,,0,0,0,karaoke,握ったメッセージ　That's Rising Hope
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.58,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,手握的信息 那是升腾的希望
Comment: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:05.20,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,（欢迎来到信息狂国）
Comment: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.08,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,（你能保持距离做好准备吗）
Comment: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:07.86,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,（开始吧）
Comment: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.26,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,静止的世界 出现异常的幻听
Comment: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.56,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,相连的手是上升的灵魂
Comment: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.98,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,不如想象那般
Comment: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.32,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,静谧骚动的本能
Comment: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.44,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,仿若迷路 没有尽头
Comment: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.70,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,思考已然扭曲
Comment: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:30.10,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,不知何时起 无法宽恕
Comment: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:32.64,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,一旦失去就将狂乱
Comment: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:35.28,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,嘿 1 2 3
Comment: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:38.40,SAO3-OP-qqw,,0,0,0,karaoke,不需要常识
